
"smart_sources:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/每日文档/09_22-周一.md": {"path":"RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/每日文档/09_22-周一.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"dmnx94","at":1769676327616},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1769374122000,"size":4181,"at":1769676327616,"hash":"dmnx94"},"blocks":{"#":[1,48],"##{1}":[1,4],"##{2}":[6,12],"##{3}":[13,15],"##{4}":[16,19],"##{5}":[20,23],"##{6}":[24,27],"##{7}":[28,31],"##{8}":[32,33],"##{9}":[34,34],"##{10}":[35,37],"##{11}":[38,48]},"outlinks":[{"title":"几何意义","target":"../几何意义.md","line":13},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$。\n\n\n- **题目**：设点$P$是曲线$y = \\sqrt{x^{2}+1}$上的动点，点$F(0,-\\sqrt{2})$，$A(\\sqrt{2},0)$满足$\\vert PF\\vert + \\vert PA\\vert = 4$，则点$P$的坐标为______。\n    - **解析**：曲线$y = \\sqrt{x^{2}+1}$对应双曲线$y^{2} - x^{2}=1$的上半部分，上焦点为$F'(0,\\sqrt{2})$。由$\\vert PF\\vert + \\vert PA\\vert = 4$及$\\vert PF\\vert - \\vert PF'\\vert = 2$，得$\\vert PF'\\vert + \\vert PA\\vert = 2$，又$\\vert AF'\\vert = 2$，故$P$、$A$、$F'$共线，联立直线$x + y = \\sqrt{2}$与双曲线方程，解得$P(\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{4},\\frac{3\\sqrt{2}}{4})$。\n\n\n- **题目**：已知$P_1(x_1,y_1)$，$P_2(x_2,y_2)(x_1\\neq x_2)$是双曲线$x^{2} - y^{2}=1$上位于第一象限的任意两点，且$y_2 - y_1 = t(x_2 - x_1)$，则函数$f(t)=\\frac{y_1}{2^{y_1}+1}$的值域为______。\n    - **解析**：双曲线渐近线斜率为$1$，故$t\\in(1,+\\infty)$。将$f(t)$变形为$1 - \\frac{1}{2^{y_1}+1}$，因函数为增函数，故值域为$(\\frac{1}{3},1)$。\n- ![","target":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/hQ4_SlufdZw2GV9os05BVm_fzK1JhMI6eKStUnxHmeYmMyU35midodOYPfW7cabpDWLoz2TwI-5TKXCGd-GkSsPbypZpXADyRFfw903dfw9JAOP0FB6cVSfXbPXdr96-.png","line":25}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
